asis-are-going-head-to-head-with-sabrina-carpenter-for-this-weeks-uk-number-one-single-3789714">与Oasis进行了一场持续的排行榜战中</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sabrina-carpenter-and-jenna-ortega-in-horror-inspired-taste-teaser-3785996">与Jenna Ortega合作，</a>为她的最新单曲“ Taste&#39;进行音乐录影带，成为头条新闻。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-fans-are-not-happy-about-sabrina-carpenters-crumbl-cookies-collaboration-3789757">Olivia Rodrigo的帖子对Sabrina Carpenter的Crumbl Cookies合作不满意，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
